Package org.frc5010.common.config

Class DriveteamControllerConfiguration

java.lang.Object
org.frc5010.common.config.DriveteamControllerConfiguration
public class DriveteamControllerConfiguration extends Object
A class for storing configuration data for a single controller.
  • port: The port number of the controller.
  • axes: The axes of the controller.
